lead_paragraph: Patrick Maroon scored twice and the Edmonton Oilers won at Rexall Place for the final time, beating the Vancouver Canucks 6-2 on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Oilers Rout Canucks 6-2 in Final Game at Rexall Place
